data.description: 3 story, coastal designed home boasting ocean, sunset & launch views and just a 3 minute walk from the beach! Built as a single family residence, but designed for flexible use with 4 independent living spaces to allow single family, multigenerational or as an income producing property. 5 bdrms (2 primary suites), 4 full baths, 4 kitchens & 3 full laundry set ups. The ground floor was designed with handicap accessibility in mind and also features 3 different patios from which to access a spacious .42 acre property with high end Zoysia sports turf and lush native landscaping + ample RV & boat parking. NEW Roof (7/23), & multiple other recent updates & always built with strict attention to coastal demands, this home will grant years of low maintenance service! Assumable 2.75% mortgage!
